text: A:Yes, immigrants in registered provisional immigrant status would be permitted to travel abroad for up to 180 days #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:While waiting in the US for a status adjustment, can an immigrant travel abroad & return to the US? – Deana Moreno #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: A:Yes, our bill strengthens border security & helps prevent crime. $3-6bil for better tech on the border, fencing & security #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:There seems to be a lot of crime from our southern borders. Will #immigration reform make this better? – Kyle Bracken #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: A: There's a simpler process for #DREAMers who received Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals (DACA), not auto- legalization. #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:Will ppl w/already-approved work permits from the recent DACA prgm be automatically legalized?–Raquel from Oklahoma City #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: A: Best #DreamAct ever in #Gangof8 bill. #DREAMers could apply for residency (then citizenship) after 5yrs w/provisional status #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:Will #DREAMers be affected by the reform or will they gain residency at a faster rate? – Maria Santana #AskMenendez #LATISM #ImReadyVL
name: Bob Menendez

text: A:If you've had TPS (or other temp status) for 10yrs+, you'd be immediately eligible for a green card & 3yrs later-citizenship. #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:I have Temporary Protected Status (TPS). Will I have to wait 13 years to become a US citizen ? – Aracely Chinchilla #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: A:We give DHS case-by-case discretion 4 torn apart fams & help stop states from ending parental rights based on parents' status #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:What happens to separated families who've had kids put in the system bc no one could take them to their parents?–Kesley Umana #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: A:Immediately reunifies green card holder w/spouse & minor kids. Helps deported families reunite & speeds process 4 ppl waiting #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:What does the bill hope to accomplish in regards to keeping families together? – Lorena  #ImReadyVL #immigration
name: Bob Menendez

text: A: @amprog estimates our bill could add $832bil to GDP over 10yrs. Plus, more legal future #immigration adds another $1.8 tril+.#AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q: What are its economic benefits? – @RighttoFood1 RE: #immigration reform. #AskMenendez cc: #CIR #Gangof8 #LATISM #ImReadyVL #TimeIsNow
name: Bob Menendez

text: A: Associated immigration fees & fines fund enforcement & other provisions of #Gangof8 bill. Should be no cost to taxpayers. #AskMenendez
name: Bob Menendez

text: Q:How much will it cost taxpayers to enforce new #immigration laws? – Nancy Macario #AskMenendez

text: A:The House should debate Sen bill-big GOP names support it. But whether Sen bill or combo, Americans want fix to broken system #AskMenendez
